99
00:04:30,220 --> 00:04:33,820
They had unbelief and we were able to learn those things.

100
00:04:33,820 --> 00:04:37,779
But now as we begin to consider the consequences of doubt,

101
00:04:37,779 --> 00:04:40,619
I hope that it would help us to have

102
00:04:40,619 --> 00:04:42,859
