198
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:35,640
it says that the whole congregation,

199
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:39,320
all the children of Israel, it says all the congregation

200
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:40,919
bade stone them with stones.

